The unexpected happened in Mellen Gabon, Central Africa recently as a young woman was delivered of a baby on a grass after she was unable to pay hospital bill.
According to agency reports, the woman was said to have given birth in the open air on the grass outside the regional hospital of Mellen in Gabon.
“The woman was taken to the hospital to give birth but refused to pay the amount the hospital asked for the delivery.
The hospital then refused to attend to her and shut their doors on her.
“While outside the hospital, the baby came and some women around helped her with the delivery.
The name of the woman and sex of the baby were not disclosed.
